        </div>
   </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> - Field 540 ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present. If the final
                     subfield is subfield $5, the mark of punctuation precedes that subfield.
      </div>
      <hr>
      <h3>CONTENT DESIGNATOR HISTORY</h3>
      <div class="font_small"><em>$u - Uniform Resource Identifier [NEW, 2002]</em></div>
